  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Why is it always the innocents who suffer most, when you high lords play your <b>game of thrones</b>?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Ned Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_58\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 58\">Chapter 58</a>, Eddard XV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403104349\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 90/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 306/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 525/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.229      1 -total\n100.00%    4.229      1 Template:Ref\n 65.62%    2.775      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2933-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403104349 and revision id 275289\n -->\n",
